		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//kristof.blogs.nytimes.com/2017/11/22/how-to-use-twitter/" data-title="How to Use Twitter" data-description="Start by listening. If you&#039;re wrong, acknowledge it.">
